WBdata$type<-factor(WBdata$type, levels=c("WT", "Control", "tepsin", "AP4E1"))
WBdata$BvsS<-factor(WBdata$BvsS, levels=c("Basal", "Starved"))
library(ggplot2)

library(ggpattern)
library(viridis)

plotme<-function(yaxis,labelme,mytitle,nameme){
   ggplot(WBdata,aes(x=type,y=yaxis,fill=type, pattern=BvsS)) + 
      geom_bar_pattern(binaxis='y', width=.5, position = position_dodge(0.9),alpha=.5, stat = "identity",
              color = "black", 
              pattern_fill = "black",
              pattern_angle = 45,
              pattern_density = 0.1,
              pattern_spacing = 0.025,
              pattern_key_scale_factor = 0.6) + 
                guides(pattern = guide_legend(override.aes = list(fill = "white")),
         fill = guide_legend(override.aes = list(pattern = "none")))+
      #geom_dotplot(binaxis='y', stackdir='center', stackratio= 0.8, dotsize = 0.25, position = position_dodge(0.9),alpha=.5)+
      ylab(labelme)+
      ggtitle(mytitle)+
      theme_minimal()+
      theme(plot.title=element_text(hjust=.5))+
        scale_fill_viridis(discrete=TRUE,end=.9) +
        scale_color_viridis(discrete=TRUE,end=.9)+
        scale_pattern_manual(values = c(Basal = "none", Starved = "stripe"))
  
}
